{#
Template to process the bad renew mail that recurring payments module will send.
Available variables:
      - 'order_items': an array with the expiring items in order.
      - 'user': the customer object.
      - 'order_entity': the order entity object.
      - 'renew_url': the url to renew the purchase.
#}
Hello {{ user.label }},
<br/>
These items in {{ 'order #@number'|t({'@number': order_entity.getOrderNumber}) }} have been expired and cannot be automatically renewed:
<br/>
{{ order_items|length }}
{% for order_item in order_items %}
- <span>#{{ order_item.id }} - {{ order_item.label }}</span>
{% endfor %}

<br />
You could review the orders in {{ renew_url }}.


